comments: if you like crawling around the floor & looking ridiculous, by all means take this class. saba is very interesting & encouraging. class was definitely easy; however do not take this class if you do not want to be put on the spot!
This class is so much fun if you get into it. You get what you put into it. Saba is super fun and easy going as long as you participate so do itttttt:)

i really liked her. she was really sweet and very encouraging to everyone. yes there is workbook work and papers to turn in from watching the plays. she didnt make you sign in for attendance but trust me, she knows when you\'re not there. overall she was a cool teacher.
